5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Passport size photos</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;', 'proprietorship', 'Proprietorship Registration - Startup with SmartFilings', 'Complete your proprietorship registration online in less than 48 hours anywhere from India. Proprietorship startup with GST registration and IT filing starting at less than Rs.1999 per year.', 'Proprietorship Registration, Sole Proprietorship, Proprietorship Firm Registration, Register a Proprietorship, Start a Proprietorship, Proprietorship Registration in vellore, company registration proprietorship firm, proprietary company registration, proprietorship company registration online, register proprietorship company online, register proprietorship firm online, business registration for sole proprietorship, online registration for proprietorship firm, register your sole proprietor business, firm registration for proprietorship, sole company registration, company registration proprietorship, proprietorship company registration, sole proprietorship registration for online business, register my sole proprietorship, individual firm registration, sole proprietorship application, sole proprietorship company registration, register business name sole trader, sole proprietorship firm registration online, register company sole proprietorship, proprietorship firm registration online, business name registration for sole proprietorship, proprietorship business registration, registration of proprietorship firm online, proprietorship registration cost, register proprietorship firm, new proprietorship firm registration, sole prop registration, proprietorship registration online, sole proprietorship registration online, sole proprietorship business registration, gst for sole proprietorship, proprietorship firm registration mca, gstin registration for proprietorship, msme sole proprietorship registration, single proprietorship registration, msme proprietorship registration, gst for proprietorship, register sole proprietorship online, gst apply for proprietorship, gst registration sole proprietorship, proprietorship firm registration, sole proprietorship registration cost, gst registration for sole proprietorship firm, gst registration for proprietorship online, sole proprietorship registration, register sole proprietorship, udyog aadhar for sole proprietorship, registering a business sole proprietorship, proprietorship registration, sole proprietorship firm registration, open a proprietorship firm, register gst for proprietorship, gst registration proprietorship, proprietorship register, cost to register sole proprietorship, cost of registering sole proprietorship, firm registration proprietorship, gst proprietorship registration, proprietorship gst registration, cost of proprietorship firm registration, proprietorship firm gst registration, gst registration for proprietorship, apply gst for proprietorship firm, proprietorship gst, gst registration for sole proprietorship, gst registration for proprietorship firm, gst registration of proprietorship, gst for proprietorship firm, new gst registration for proprietorship, gst registration online for sole proprietorship, gst proprietorship, msme sole proprietorship, smart filings, proprietorship in {city}', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, 1999, 1500, 499, 0, 6999, 1500, 999, 0, 8999, 8000, '999', 'Included', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
(2, 1, 13, '', 'partnership firm', 'Get your partnership registered with India\'s leading platform starting.', 'Partnership deed drafting , mSME with GST registration', 'Partnership Deed Drafting , MSME With GST Registration , 1-year GST return filing', 'Partnership Deed Drafting , MSME With GST Registration , 1-Year GST Return Filing , income tax filing', '<h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.31818em; font-size: 3.14286em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	How to register a Partnership firm in India?</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Partnership firm registration is required when two or more parties sign a formal agreement to manage and operate a business and share both the profits and losses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Registering a Partnership is the right choice for small enterprises as the formation is straightforward and there are minimal regulatory compliances.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The Partnership Act has been in existence in India since 1932, making partnerships one of the oldest types of business entities in India. A partnership firm can even be registered after it is formed. There are as such no penalties for non Registration of a Partnership firm. But unregistered Partnership firms are denied certain rights under section 69 of the Partnership Act that majorly deals with the effects of non Registration of Partnership firms.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"nav_link_3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Types of Partnership firm</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Depending on the extent of the liability while Partnership firm registration, we can derive the different classes of partners.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Partnership Firms can be classified into two types registered and unregistered Partnership firms. The Indian Partnership Act states that the only criterion to commence the business as a Partnership firm is a finalization and the partnership deed&#39;s execution between the Partners.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Under this act, the Partnership firms don&#39;t need to be registered. As an outcome of this lot of partnership businesses exist as unregistered partnership firms.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	There are no penalties for the nonregistration of the partnership firms. Also, a partnership firm can be registered even after formation. But the unregistered partnership firms have been denied certain rights in Section 69 of the Partnership Act, which deals majorly with the effects of the non-registration of the partnership firm.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Here are the reasons why an individual should opt for a registered partnership firm:</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	A registered firm partner cannot file suit in any court against the firm or other partners for the enforcement of any right arising from a contract or right conferred by the Partnership Act.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	No suit to enforce a right arising from an agreement can be instituted in any court by or on behalf of a firm against any third party unless the firm is registered under the Partnership Act.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	An unregistered firm or any of its partners cannot claim set-off or other proceedings in a dispute with a third party.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Therefore, it is better to register a Partnership sooner or later.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 3999, '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 40px; display: table; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Partnership Deed</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Stamp Paper Purchase&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 10.56px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">1</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		MSME Reg</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		GST Registration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 40px; display: table; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Partnership Deed</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Stamp Paper Purchase&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		MSME Reg</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		GST Registration</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		GST Filings 1 Year</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 11999, '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 40px; display: table; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Partnership Deed</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Stamp Paper Purchase&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		MSME Reg</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		GST Registration</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		GST Filings 1 Year</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		IT Filing&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '02-02-2022-11-23-45-am2.jpg', 1, 8999, '<h2 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nav_link_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	What documents are required to register a Partnership Firm In India?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	The application for the Partnership registration form must include the prescribed documents like the Identity proof, address proof, a real copy of the Partnership deed entered into and the proof of the Principal place of business.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Any of the following documents can be submitted as identity proof and address proofs.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f p-l-30 ul_f_f_decimal\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); padding-left: 30px !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		PAN card</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Passport</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Driver License</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Aadhar Card</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Voters ID</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Proof of Business premise can be established by submitting the following documents:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f p-l-30 m-b-0 ul_f_f_decimal\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding-left: 30px !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Sale Deed in case if the Partner owns the place</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Rental agreement copy if the office is on rental basis</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Copy of the latest electricity bill or the tax bill receipt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 class=\"title_div\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: normal; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: roboto; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	Benefits of a Partnership</h2>\r\n<div class=\"avatar_div first\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-top: 25px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	<div class=\"avatarcontent\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 25px;\">\r\n		<p class=\"title_header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 17px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n			Minimum Compliance</p>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n			For General Partnerships, there is no need for an auditor to be appointed or, if the company is still in the process of registration or incase unregistered, annual accounts filing with the registrar is not necessary either. When compared to LLP, annual compliances are also fewer. Further, taxes depending on turnover, service and sales tax also need not be filed in General Partnerships.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"avatar_div \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	<div class=\"avatarcontent\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 25px;\">\r\n		<p class=\"title_header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 17px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n			Simple To Begin</p>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n			General Partnerships can begin simply with an unregistered deed of the partnership within 2-4 business days. However, having registration for the same has its own perks and advantages. The primary advantage for having a registered firm is that it will allow you to book lawsuits in courtrooms opposing another business or the business associates in the firm for the administration of rights addressed in the Partnership Act.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"avatar_div \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	<div class=\"avatarcontent\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 25px;\">\r\n		<p class=\"title_header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 17px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n			Comparatively Economical</p>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n			In comparison to LLP, a General Partnership is much cheaper to begin. Even in the longer run, it will still work out inexpensive as the compliance requirements are very minimal. For example, there is no need for an auditor. Therefore, Home businesses still opt for this, although it offers unlimited liability.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'partnership-firm', 'Partnership Firm Registration - Startup with Smart Filings', 'Step by step guide on how to register a Partnership firm online in India, partnership firm registration fees and download partnership registration certificate', 'partnership firm, partnership firm registration online, partnership deed, partnership deed format partnership registration , partnership registration, partnership deed, partnership agreement, partnership deed registration, partnership firm process and procedure, firm registration online, what is partnership, incorporate partnership, partnership firm, partnership firm registration, partnership firm process and procedure, what is partnership, how to register a firm, how to register a partnership firm, procedure of registration of partnership firm, partnership firm registration process, formation of partnership, registration of partnership firm under Indian partnership, register partnership firm, what is partnership firm, Partnership Firm Registration in vellore, smart filings', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
