ht: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n		Two Directors:</p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">A private limited company must have at least two directors and at most, there can be 15 directors. Among all the directors in the business, at least one must be a resident of India.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"description_data\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	<p class=\"heading_text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 17px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n		Unique Name</p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The name of your business must be unique. The suggested name should not match with any existing companies or trademarks in India.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"description_data\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	<p class=\"heading_text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 17px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n		Minimum Capital Contribution:</p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">There is no minimum capital amount for a company. A company should have an authorized capital of at least Rs. 1 lakh.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"description_data\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">\r\n	<p class=\"heading_text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 17px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\">\r\n		Registered Office:</p>\r\n	<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The registered office of a company does not have to be a commercial space. Even a rented home can be the registered office, so long as an NOC is obtained from the landlord.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 6000, '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 15px; display: table; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 25px;\">\r\n		2 Digital Signature - 2 Year Validity&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 10.56px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">1</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 25px;\">\r\n		2 Director Identification Numbers</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 25px;\">\r\n		Name Approval&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 10.56px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">2</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 25px;\">\r\n		Authorised Capital Fee&nbsp;<span st