; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 10px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n			Rather than a single farmer managing their entire business, producer companies&#39; work is divided among the directors. The entity is governed by the Management Board, which has a tenure of five years.</p>\r\n		<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n			A producer company has a separate legal existence, which means that it is not affected by any of its members&#39; death.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'producer-company', 'Producer Company', 'Registering Farmer Agro Producer Company Online in India takes up to 15 days and its cost Rs. 43899. Find all you need to know about producer company in India.', 'Producer Company, Farmer Producer Company Registration in India, features of producer company, Incorporation of Producer Company, farmer producer company registration process, farmer producer company act, producer certificate format, producer certificate format for producer company, agro producer company, farmer producer company online, producer company registration, get cooperative society registration, whether producer company is tax exempted, farmer producer company registration process, farmer producer company registration, producer company incorporation, producer company registration fees, farmer producer organization registration process, producer company registration process, producer company registration online, agro producer company registration, farmer producer company registration fees, farmer producer company registration documents, procedure for incorporation of producer company, documents required for farmer producer company, producer card online registration, registration of farmer producer company, producer company formation, producer company incorporation fees, documents required for producer company, producer company registration procedure, documents required for incorporation of producer company, farmer producer company online registration, smart filings, Producer Company in vellore', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL);
