: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">\r\n			How to obtain Digital Signature for Directors?</h2>\r\n		<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n			In India, a Trust is controlled by the trustees mentioned in the Trust Deed. Section 8 Company will be governed by the Board of Directors, similar to a Private Limited Company.</p>\r\n		<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n			During the process of incorporation, the DSC is obtained for the proposed directors. The following documents must be submitted.</p>\r\n		<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14.08px; padding-left: 30px !important;\">\r\n			<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n				PAN or Aadhar card.</li>\r\n			<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n				Drivers License/ Passport/ Election ID/ Government Issued ID.</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p class=\"text-justify m-b-40\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 40px !important;\">\r\n			After submitting these documents, the applicant must complete an OTP and eKYC procedure to obtain a DSC in their name.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Details of Director</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Address Proof</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Who can Incorporate a Section 8 Company?</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	An individual or group of individuals can apply for Section 8 Company Registration if it holds the below-mentioned intentions. The objectives have to be confirmed to the satisfaction of the Central Government.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30 m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		If the company intends to promote science, commerce, education, art, sports, research, charity, social welfare, protection of the environment, or other objectives</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		If the company has the intention to invest all the profits or the income generated after incorporation in the promotion of such objects only;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		When the company is not intending to pay any dividends to its members.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'section-8-company', 'Section 8 Company', 'Section 8 Company can be registered for charitable purposes. Sectio