: 0px;\">\r\n		Photographs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" id=\"nav_link_5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">\r\n	USA Entry strategies</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Business in the US can be set up in sole proprietorship, general partnership, LLC, or a Corporation. However, the entries for Indian companies are limited to an LLC or a C corporation in the USA.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	In the USA, the laws and the regulations relevant to the Incorporation and management of LLC or corporation differ from one state to another. We incorporate all LLC or Corporations for Indian Nationals in Delaware as Company registration in Delaware has various benefits like low taxes, minimal maintenance fees, and excellent corporate laws.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-25\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); margin-bottom: 25px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Well, incorporating in Delaware is not only a good option for Indian Nationals and companies, but even American Companies as more than half of the companies are publicly traded, and fortune 500 companies in the USA are incorporated in Delaware.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	LLC (Limited Liability Company)</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	LLC is a type of entity that has features of both corporation and a partnership. LLC provides the owners limited liability protection in case of a lawsuit and even bankruptcy. LLCs are more flexible, and the compliance requirements for LLC are simple.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-25\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); margin-bottom: 25px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	A corporation requires resolutions and shareholders meetings and the recording and filing of forms showing meetings that were held and votes. On the contrary, LLCs do not require annual shareholders&#39; meetings.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	C-Corporation</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	If the goal is to seek funding from the VCs and angel investors, it is better to seek a C corporation in the USA. The bankers, investors, customers, suppliers, and employees consider corporations ideal for most businesses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	C-Corporations independent legal entities that are separate from the people who own, control, and manage. Due to this, it is viewed as a regular person in tax laws and can thus be engaged in business, and contracts can initiate lawsuits and be sued.</p>\r\n', 'usa-company-registration', 'USA Company Registration', 'Online USA company registration for Indian nationals and businesses without physical presence in USA. Register an LLC or a C-Corporation in the USA in less than 5 working days and obtain EIN Number (Employer Identification Number) through smartFilings.', 'USA Company Registration, USA LLC Registration, Incorporate Your Business in USA, LLC Filing USA, Business Formation in USA, Company Registration in USA, How to Start a Company in the USA, How to Register a company in USA, Register your business in USA, Small Business Registration in USA, USA company registration from India, Process to register a company in the USA, How to Open a Company in the USA, USA company registration for non residents, company registration in usa for foreign llc, company registration in USA, How much does it cost to register a company in USA, us company registration, offshore company registration in us, register company in usa from india, llc company registration in usa, company registration in usa for foreign, register a company in usa non resident, us company registration for non-residents, commercial register usa, register business in usa, usa company registration from india, us commercial register, registered agent usa, offshore company registration in usa, company registration certificate usa, check company registration usa, company registration in usa for non-residents, register business usa, us company registration certificate, register us company online, online company registration in usa, register your company in usa, register a company name in usa, register a company in the usa for foreigner, register business us non resident, company registration cost in usa, register us company non resident, virtual company registration in usa, company registration process in usa, register business name in usa, smart filings,', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL);
