(20, 1, 14, '', 'Copyright Registration', 'Copyright Registration', 'Copyright registration for logos, books, periodicals and magazines.', 'Copyright registration for videos, audio recording and cinematography films.', 'Copyright registration for logos, books, periodicals, magazines,videos, audio recording, cinematography films with trademark registration.', '<h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.31818em; font-size: 3.14286em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	Copyright Registration Documents, Benefits Eligibility, Process &amp; Validity</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Copyright is the right of ownership entitled to literature, drama, music, artworks, sound recordings, etc. Copyright registration grants a bundle of rights that comprise rights to reproduction, communication to the public, adaptation, and translation of the work. Registering a Copyright ensures certain minimum safeguards of the rights of ownership and enjoyment of the authors over their creations, which protects and rewards creativity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	It is necessary to register for copyright because it makes you communicate to the public, reproduce the rights, adapt and translate the works.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Lately, there has been a substantial increase in the amount of intellectual property being registered in India as the awareness about intellectual property laws has increased. Copyright registration happens to be one of the critical types of intellectual types of property protection.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Copyright registration is done as per the regulations of the Copyright Act,1957. The author&#39;s creative work cannot be copied as no person is allowed to use the same without the permission of the author or the creator. The author can charge others for using or changing his work. The copyright protection typically lasts for 60 years.</p>\r\n', 12899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Copyright registration for logos, books, periodicals and magazines.</span>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Copyright registration for videos, audio recording and cinematography films.</span>', 18899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Copyright registration for logos, books, periodicals, magazines,videos, audio recording, cinematography films with trademark registration.</span>', '02-02-2022-11-51-19-amcopyright-registration.jpg', 1, 14899, '<p class=\"text-justify m-b-5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 5px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	To obtain copy registration, the following documents should be submitted:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30 m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Name, address, and nationality of the candidate- Id Proof</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		NOC from the publisher if the publisher and the applicant are two different individuals</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Search Certificate from Trademark office if any</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		NOC from a person whose photograph appears on the work</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Power of attorney</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		2 Copies of the work (Book / Source code in CD (if Website copyright))</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		KYC of author</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" id=\"nav_link_2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Eligibility</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 5px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Copyright registration can be obtained for any works related to literature, drama, music, artwork, film, or sound recording. Copyrights are given to mainly three classes of work, and each class has its distinctive right under the copyright act.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30 m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Original literary, dramatic, musical, and artistic works comprise the copyright for books, music, painting, sculpture, etc.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Cinematography films are another class of copyright that consists of any work of visual recording on any medium.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Sound recordings have a distinctive class under the copyright act that consists of a recording of sounds, regardless of the medium on which such recording is made or the method by which the sound is produced.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'copyright-registration', 'Copyright Registration', 'Get copyright registration online in India for books, music, film, photography and software applications and etc. through smartFilings.', 'Copyright Registration, Copyright registration in vellore, copyright filing, register a copyright, smartfiligs, copyright application, register copyright, copyright filing, online copyright registration, logo copyright registration, dmca registration, copyright and trademark registration, international copyright registration, global copyright registry, copyright office registration, register logo copyright, copyright registration service, dmca registered agent, application for registration of copyright, copyright registered trademark, music copyright registration, register music copyright, copyright registration cost, screenplay copyright registration, register copyright online, website copyright registration, electronic copyright registration, copyright office electronic system, registration of copyright slideshare, office of copyright registration, copyright registration application, dmca agent registration, register copyright and trademark, register song copyright, cost to register copyright, expedited copyright registration, song copyright registration, software copyright registration, copyright and trademark online registration, federal copyright and trademark registration, brand copyright registration, script copyright registration, eu copyright registration, register your copyright, copyright and registered trademark, gov copyright registration, copyright group registration, group copyright registration, product copyright registration, register my copyright, trademark copyright registration, the global copyright registry, government copyright registration, submit copyright application, register your music copyright, story copyright registration, registration of a copyright, cipc copyright registration, smart filings,', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
(21, 1, 14, '', 'Design Registration', 'Design Registration', 'Design registration for one article, wherein the applicant is a proprietor or individual. Inclusive of government fee and service tax.', 'Design registration for one article, wherein the applicant is a legal entity having MSME or Startup registration. Inclusive of government fee and service tax.', 'Design registration for one article. Inclusive of government fee and service tax.', '<h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.31818em; font-size: 3.14286em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	Design Registration</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Design registration is a type of intellectual property protection under which a newly created design applied to an article created under an industrial process can be protected from counterfeiting. Design registration provides the creator exclusive rights to use the design for ten years, which can be further extended for five years.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 5px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	A shape, configuration, pattern or ornament, or composition of lines and colors or combination applied to any article can be registered under the Design Act,2000. But for a design to get registered, it must satisfy the following conditions:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		It should be new and original.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		The design should relate to shape, configuration, pattern, or ornament applied to an article.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		The design must be applied to any article by an industrial process.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		The design must be visible and should appear in the article.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-25\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 25px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Under the Design Act, the owner of a registered design can seek legal remedy in case of infringement.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.68421em; font-size: 1.35714em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	Definition of Design</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	A design is defined under Section 2(d) of the Designs Act 2001, as only the features of a shape, pattern, configuration, composition, or ornament of lines or colors that are applied to any article that is two dimensional, three dimensional, or both by an industrial process or any means whether mechanical, manual or chemical, separated or combined, which in the finished article are judged solely by the eye; but is not taken into account upon the principle of construction or anything which is in substance a merely mechanical device.</p>\r\n', 7899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Design registration for one article, wherein the applicant is a proprietor or individual. Inclusive of government fee and service tax.</span>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Design registration for one article, wherein the applicant is a legal entity having MSME or Startup registration. Inclusive of government fee and service tax.</span>', 12899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Design registration for one article. Inclusive of government fee and service tax.</span>', '02-02-2022-11-52-37-amdesign-registration.jpg', 1, 9899, '<p class=\"text-justify m-b-5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 5px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Following documents are to be submitted to get design registration:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		A certified copy of the original or certified copies of extracts from the disclaimer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Affidavits</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Declaration</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Other public documents can be made available on payment of a fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The affidavit should be in paragraph form and should contain a declaration of truth and verifiability. However, the cost involved in design registration may be regulated by the controller according to the fourth schedule.</p>\r\n', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" id=\"nav_link_3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">\r\n	Difference between Design Registration and Trademark</h2>\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 1110px; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px;\">\r\n	<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 1110px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">\r\n		<thead style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n			<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n				<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(222, 226, 230); border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); border-right-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); border-left-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;\">\r\n					Design Registration</th>\r\n				<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(222, 226, 230); border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); border-right-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); border-left-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;\">\r\n					Trademark</th>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n			<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n				<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n					A design registration would enable the protection of the physical appearance of a distinctive product you are planning to sell to the public (so long as that appearance does not affect the product&#39;s function in any way)</td>\r\n				<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n					A trademark would defend the symbols or words you use to identify the product as coming from your specific business.</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n				<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n					A design registration protects any new and innovative ornamental design of an article of manufacture.</td>\r\n				<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n					Trademark registration protects a word or words, name, symbol, or drawing used in commerce to distinguish one source of goods or services from that of another.</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	In certain conditions, both forms of protection may be accessible to cover a single design, providing potential rewards for these rights owners.</p>\r\n', 'design-registration', 'Design Registration', 'Get design registration online in India with smartFilings. Also, learn about document required and Registration process for design registration.', 'Design Registration, Design Registration in vellore, Design Filing, smart filings, dmca registered agent, registered design, industrial design registration, registration of industrial design, find a registered design, international design registration, european design registration, eu design registration, eu registered design, design registration number, wipo design registration, design patent registration, registered industrial design, design registration online, cipc design registration, design registration cost, logo design trademark registration, registration of trademarks patents and design, eu design register, logo patent registration, ipo design registration,', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL);
