(28, 1, 15, '', 'Temporary GST Registration', 'Temporary GST Registration', 'Completely managed GST registration service until obtaining GSTIN with Expert Support. Inclusive of all government fee and taxes.', 'Completely managed GST registration service and GST return filing service for 3 months with Expert Support. Inclusive of all government fee and taxes.', 'Completely managed GST registration service and GST return filing service for 6 months with Expert Support. Inclusive of all government fee and taxes.', '<h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.31818em; font-size: 42px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	Casual Taxable Persons: Documents Required, Process &amp; Exemption</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	A taxable person under GST is anyone who is registered under GST or required to be registered under GST. Various criteria&rsquo;s like turnover, business activity or transaction have been specified in the GST Act, which details persons liable to be registered under GST. Further, any person having registration under Service Tax, VAT or Central Excise on the date of GST coming into force will automatically be considered a taxable person under GST.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.68421em; font-size: 1.35714em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	Who is a casual taxable person under GST registration?</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Casual taxable persons or occasional taxpayers are given special treatment under GST.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The Goods and Service Tax Act defines a casual taxable person as a person who occasionally undertakes transactions that involve the supply of goods or services or both.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Hence, individuals running temporary businesses in fairs or exhibitions or seasonal businesses will need to get casual taxable person GST registration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Casual taxable person GST registration is necessary irrespective of the annual turnover, and the process must be initiated at least five days before the business undertaking. GST registration application for casual taxable persons can be made using FORM GST REG-01.</p>\r\n', 988, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Completely managed GST registration service until obtaining GSTIN with Expert Support. Inclusive of all government fee and taxes.</span>', 'Completely Managed GST Registration Service And GST Return Filing Service For 3 Months With Expert Support. Inclusive Of All Government Fee And Taxes.', 9899, 'Completely Managed GST Registration Service And GST Return Filing Service For 6 Months With Expert Support. Inclusive Of All Government Fee And Taxes.', '02-02-2022-12-18-15-pmTEMP-GST-REG.jpg', 1, 2899, '<ul class=\"p-l-15 ul_f_f list-icon list-icon-check list-icon-colored text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Scanned copy of PAN (Indian National)</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Scanned copy of Passport (for Foreign Nationals and NRIs)</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Scanned copy of Voter&rsquo;s Id/ Passport/ Driver&rsquo;s license</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Scanned Passport sized photograph.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Mobile Number</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Email</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" id=\"nav_link_2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">\r\n	Process of GST Registration for Casual Taxable Person</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Similar to any other individual, GST registration is mandatory for casual taxable persons. GST registration is mandatory for all casual taxpayers. There is no threshold limit for registering as a casual taxpayer. However, the casual taxpayer cannot exercise the option of a composition scheme.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	Advance payment of the tax by the casual taxpayer</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The casual taxpayer has to make an advance deposit for the amount equivalent to the estimated tax liability. On depositing the amount, an acknowledgment should be electronic to the applicant in the Form GST REG 02. The casual taxable person will be able to make taxable supplies only after the issuance of the certificate of registration.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	Returns filing</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Similar to the regular taxpayer, a casual taxpayer is required to file the monthly/ quarterly return Form- GSTR 1 and GSTR - 3B.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	The validity of the registration certificate</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The registration certificate as a casual taxable person is valid for the period specified by the taxpayer or 90 days from the effective day of the registration, whichever is earlier. The taxpayer can seek an extension on the given certificate by making an advance deposit of the tax amount that is equivalent to the estimated tax liability ( that is liable for the extended period).</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n	Refund of the advance deposited</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 5px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The casual taxable person is eligible for the refund of any balance of the advance tax deposited by him after adjusting his tax liability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The balance advance tax can be refunded only after all the returns are filed.</p>\r\n', 'temporary-gst-registration', 'Temporary GST Registration', 'Temporary GST Registration Online With Expert Support Through SmartFilings. A temporary GST Registration Can Be done At Anytime Due To Various Reasons Like Business Closure, Transfer Of Business Or Change Of Constitution.', 'Temporary GST Registration, temporary gst registration in vellore, temporary gst number, gst temporary registration number, temporary reference number gst, gst temporary registration, temporary gstin number, gst temporary reference number, temporary registration under gst, temporary gst registration for exhibition, temporary registration in gst, smart filings, ', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
(29, 1, 15, '', 'GST Registration Cancellation', 'GST Registration Cancellation', 'Completely managed GST registration cancellation service with Expert Support. Applicable for entities with no activities.', 'Completely managed GST registration cancellation service with Expert Support and filing of last GST return.', 'Completely managed GST registration cancellation service with Expert Support, filing of last GST return and responding to any notice', '<h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.31818em; font-size: 3.14286em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	GST Registration Cancellation</h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"lead\" id=\"nav_link_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 400;\">\r\n	How to cancel GST registration?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	GST registration can be canceled by the registered person or by the GST officer, or by the registered person&#39;s legal heirs in case of death of the person under GST. GST registration cancellation means that the person will not be registered under GST anymore, and he will not have to pay or collect GST.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	GST registration can be canceled by a GST officer or voluntarily by the person registered under GST. The taxpayer will not pay GST anymore if he cancels the GST registration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	If an individual is still carrying out business after surrendering the GST registration, it will be an offense under GST, and heavy penalties are applicable. There will be no requirement to furnish any GST return.</p>\r\n', 2899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Completely managed GST registration cancellation service with Expert Support. Applicable for entities with no activities.</span>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Completely managed GST registration cancellation service with Expert Support and filing of last GST return</span>', 9899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">Completely managed GST registration cancellation service with Expert Support, filing of last GST return and responding to any notice.</span>', '02-02-2022-12-19-27-pmGST-CANCELLATION.jpg', 1, 3899, 'Need GST Number', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" id=\"nav_link_2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Who can cancel the GST registration?</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	A GST registration can be canceled by an officer, if:</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		The registered person under GST does not conduct any business from the declared place of business or</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Issues invoice or bill without supply of goods or services violating the GST ACT or GST rules.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		If the person having GST registration has not filed GST returns for six months</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Before the cancellation of registration, the Officer would issue a notice to the taxpayer whose GST registration is liable to be canceled, requiring show cause within seven working days from the date of service of such notice.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The registered person can reply to the show cause notice within the prescribed time, or the GST registration can stand canceled.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Voluntary cancellation by the registered person</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	GST registration cancellation can be initiated by the person registered under GST under Section 29 of the CGST Act under the following circumstances:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_f_f ul_f_f_decimal text-justify p-l-30 m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: decimal; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding-left: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Discontinuance or closure of a business</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Transfer of business, amalgamation, merger, de-merger, lease, or other pertinent reasons.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Change in the constitution of business, which results in a change of PAN.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Turnover reduces below the threshold limit of GST registration.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Death of the sole proprietor</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Any other reason, the likes of which must be proved in the application.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'gst-registration-cancellation', 'GST Registration Cancellation', 'Easily surrender or cancel a GST registration online with Expert support through smartFilings. A GST registration can be cancelled at anytime due to various reasons like business closure, transfer of business or change of constitution.', 'GST Registration Cancellation, gst cancellation, how to cancel gst registration, cancellation of gst registration, how to activate cancelled gst registration, gst registration cancellation, cancel gst registration, procedure for cancellation of gst registration, revocation of cancellation of gst registration, gst cancellation, cancellation of gst registration, gst registration cancellation, cancel gst registration, gst cancellation status, gst cancellation process, surrender of gst registration, cancellation of registration under gst, procedure for cancellation of gst registration, application for cancellation of gst registration, gst surrender process, gst cancellation online, gst cancellation form, gst surrender, surrender gst number, gst registration cancellation process, gst cancellation procedure, gst number cancellation, gst cancellation status check, reason for cancellation of gst registration, gst deregistration, cancel gst number, cancellation of gst registration of composition dealer, cancellation of gst, surrender gst registration, surrender gst, new gst registration after cancellation, gst no cancellation process, cancellation of gst registration section, gst surrender rules, voluntary cancellation of gst registration, gst cancel status, time limit for cancellation of gst registration, gst registration cancellation procedure, gst cancellation form pdf, gst registration in case of death of proprietor, cancellation of gst registration for non filing of returns, gst number cancellation process, procedure to cancel gst registration, cancel my gst registration, gst no cancellation, gst registration cancellation reason, if gst registration is cancelled, gst number surrender, gst cancel registration, gst registration cancellation status, process of cancellation of gst registration, cancel gst account, gst cancellation rules, cancel gst registration process, gstin cancelled, gstin status cancelled, gst cancellation application, gst no surrender process, gst registration surrender, deactivate gst number, procedure of cancellation of gst registration, form for cancellation of gst registration, gst surrender status, closure of gst registration, documents required for cancellation of gst registration, check gst cancellation status, application for gst cancellation, gst cancellation reason, reason for gst cancellation, final return after cancellation of gst registration, procedure for gst cancellation, cancellation of gst number, gst registration surrender process, cancellation of gst registration procedure, procedure for surrender of gst registration, cancellation of gst registration by department, cancellation of gst registration without filing returns, gst registration cancellation rules, gst registration cancelled by department, gst cancelled by department, gst deactivate, cancel gst application, gst number surrender process, my gst is cancelled, GST Registration Cancellation in vellore, smart filings, ', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL);
