ox; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Business Tax Return Filing</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 235); line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		Partnership Renewal</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; line-height: 42px;\">\r\n		GST Return Filings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '02-02-2022-12-23-11-pmpartnership-firm-retrn-filing.jpg', 1, 14899, 'Partnership DED<br />\r\nSale Report<br />\r\nPurchase Report<br />\r\nGST log In<br />\r\nBank Statement&nbsp;', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	The tax rate for a Partnership firm</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	What is the tax rate for a partnership firm?</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	A partnership firm is required to file a partnership firm income tax return under the Income Tax Act,1961. Partnership firms are liable to pay income tax at the rate of 30% of total income. Besides, a partnership firm is liable to pay an income tax surcharge of 12% if the total income exceeds Rs.1 crores.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Additional to the income tax and surcharge a partnership firm must pay the education cess and the secondary higher education cess.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Education Cess is applicable on the amount of the income tax and the applicable surcharge at the rate of 2%. Secondary and higher education cess is applicable on the amount of the income tax and the applicable surcharge at the rate of 1%.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Alternative minimum tax</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Similar to a private limited company or LLP, partnership firms are also required to pay alternate minimum tax at the rate of 18.5% of &quot;adjusted total income&quot;. Alternate minimum tax would be increased by the applicable surcharge, education cess, and secondary and higher education cess.</p>\r\n', 'partnership', 'Annual Compliance - Partnership Firm', 'File income tax return for partnership firm online with Accountant support. Partnership firms are required to file tax return in form ITR-5 each financial year.', 'Partnership firm income tax return, partnership tax return filing, partnership tax filing, Partnership Firm in vellore, smart filings, itr for partnership firm, itr form for partnership firm, income tax return for partnership firm, itr 5 for partnership firm, partnership firm itr, itr filing for partnership firm, partnership firm return filing, income tax filing for partnership firm, itr form for partner in partnership firm, income tax form for partnership firm, partnership firm itr filing, itr partnership firm, partnership firm can file itr 4,', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL);
