40px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"row\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-lg-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%;\">\r\n			<h3 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n				Pre-Payroll Activities</h3>\r\n			<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n				Defining payroll policy</h3>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				The first step is wherein the policies to the bank during the payroll processes need to be established. These policies need to be approved by the management to turn these policies into standards. Policies like the Pay policy, Attendance policy, leave and benefits policy, and more.</p>\r\n			<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n				Gathering inputs</h3>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				At this stage, the inputs are gathered from various departments to ensure the accurate calculation of the payroll.</p>\r\n			<div class=\"table-responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 1110px; overflow-x: auto;\">\r\n				<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 1110px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">\r\n					<thead style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n						<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n							<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(222, 226, 230); border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); border-right-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); border-left-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Source of Data</th>\r\n							<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(222, 226, 230); border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); border-right-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); border-left-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Data Example</th>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</thead>\r\n					<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n						<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Employees</td>\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Income tax declaration, facilities availed, and more</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								HR team</td>\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Salary structure, eligibility for benefits</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Finance team</td>\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Deduction for recoveries</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Leave and attendance systems</td>\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Data from attendance systems, current work shift, etc.</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								General service providers</td>\r\n							<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230) rgb(236, 236, 236) rgb(236, 236, 236); vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">\r\n								Transport service provider, canteen vendor, etc.</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				This data collection can seem tedious at first but registering with IndiaFilings will make it more hassle-free.</p>\r\n			<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\r\n				Input validation</h3>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				It is necessary to verify the validity of the data once it is gathered as a minute mistake can ruin the entire payroll process.</p>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				It is necessary to ensure that the list contains all the active employees and no records of inactive employees. Checking the data whether it adheres to the company policy. Ensure the present in the right format.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"background-grey\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 80px 0px; position: relative; width: 1349px; overflow: hidden; z-index: 1; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251) !important;\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 15px; width: 1140px; max-width: 1140px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"row\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-lg-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%;\">\r\n			<h2 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">\r\n				Payroll Calculation</h2>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				This step is when the validated input data is fed into the payroll system for actual payroll processing. The result is the Net pay after adjusting the necessary taxes and other deductions.</p>\r\n			<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n				Once the payroll process is over it is always better to reconcile the values and verify the accuracy to avoid further errors.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Various methods of payroll management</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Excel-based payroll management</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	At the initial stage of operations and when a company has a handful of employees they opt for excel based payroll management.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	In excel based payroll management the calculation is done on excel sheets using the standard payroll calculation template. The already set mathematical formulas help the payroll officer to do the computation. But this method has many errors like</p>\r\n<ul class=\"p-l-15 ul_f_f list-icon list-icon-arrow list-icon-colored text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		High chances of clerical and mathematical errors as the data are entered manually</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Difficulty in adding and removing employees from the payroll list</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Chances of duplicate data and omission of entries at times</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		Need to monitor the tax updates and other statutory changes like the PF, PT, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Outsourcing Payroll</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	When the payroll is outsourced an external agency is taking care of the payroll function. The payroll service provider based on the pay cycle every month provides various other data such as the attendance, leaves, and reimbursement details.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The external service provider then computes the payroll and takes care of the statutory compliance. Since payroll is a crucial function IndiaFilings can help you comply with all the needs.</p>\r\n', 'payroll', 'Payroll Management', 'Outsource your payroll processing and HR management to smartFilings. Get error-free monthly payroll calculation and payslips for your employees.', 'Payroll Management, Payroll processing, payroll management in vellore, hr management, smart filings, payroll, epay roll, paycheck, mypayroll, payroll services, payroll system, payroll companies, e payroll, payroll management, hr payroll, payroll management system, payroll process, payroll in tally, payrol, cloud payroll, payroll administrator, payroll solutions, payroll accounting, payroll outsourcing, sap payroll, payroll online, workday payroll, employee payroll, payroll outsourcing services, payroll services near me, payroll sheet, payroll service providers, payroll cost, payroll hr, quick books payroll, hr and payroll, payroll outsourcing companies, payroll management services, payroll processing services, payroll process in hr, teamlease payroll, employee payroll management system, hr payroll system, payroll in tally erp 9, online attendance, 3rd party payroll, payroll preparation, osource payroll, service payroll, payroll package, payroll reporting, payroll management process, sap hr payroll, payroller, single touch payroll, mypaysolutions, certified payroll, payroll services for small business, manage payroll, eziway payroll, paycom payroll,', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
(45, 1, 17, '', 'PF Registration', 'PF Registration', 'PF registration for businesses having less than 25 employees.', 'PF registration for businesses having less than 40 employees', 'PF registration for businesses having more than 40 employees.', '<h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.31818em; font-size: 3.14286em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n	Employee Provident Fund</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Employees Provident Fund is a scheme for the Indian Employees that is controlled by the Provident Funds and Miscellaneous Provisions Act,1952. The Employee Provident Fund is regulated under the umbrella of Employees Provident Fund Organization popularly known as EPFO.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	All establishments that have employed 20 or more than 20 employees can apply for PF registration in India. In some cases subject to the circumstances and the exemption establishments employing less than 20 are still eligible for PF registration. The Employee gets an amount that includes the self and employer&rsquo;s contribution with interest on retirement or resignation.</p>\r\n', 899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">PF registration for businesses having less than 25 employees.</span>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">PF registration for businesses having less than 40 employees.</span>', 24899, '<span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: center;\">PF registration for businesses having more than 40 employees.</span>', '02-02-2022-12-37-52-pmpf-registration.jpg', 1, 14899, '<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	he employer has to attach the following documents with the registration form:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"timeline text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; position: relative; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3rem 2rem 3rem 5rem; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"timeline-icon\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(34, 80, 252); position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; left: 0px; width: 34px; height: 34px; z-index: 3; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n			1</div>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n			PAN of the Partner, Proprietor, or the Director</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3rem 2rem 3rem 5rem; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"timeline-icon\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(34, 80, 252); position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; left: 0px; width: 34px; height: 34px; z-index: 3; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n			2</div>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n			Address proof (can be any utility bill but should not be older than 2 months)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3rem 2rem 3rem 5rem; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"timeline-icon\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(34, 80, 252); position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; left: 0px; width: 34px; height: 34px; z-index: 3; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n			3</div>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n			Aadhar card of Proprietor, Partner, or Director.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3rem 2rem 3rem 5rem; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"timeline-icon\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(34, 80, 252); position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; left: 0px; width: 34px; height: 34px; z-index: 3; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n			4</div>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n			Canceled Cheque Or Bank Statement</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3rem 2rem 3rem 5rem; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"timeline-icon\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(34, 80, 252); position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; left: 0px; width: 34px; height: 34px; z-index: 3; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n			5</div>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n			Digital Signature of the Proprietor/ Partner or Director.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3rem 2rem 3rem 5rem; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"timeline-icon\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(34, 80, 252); position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; left: 0px; width: 34px; height: 34px; z-index: 3; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n			6</div>\r\n		<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n			Hired/ Rented or Leased Agreement If there is any.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 class=\"text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 2.35714em; line-height: 1.36364em; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	Who is eligible to get EPF registration?</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	For Employer</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	PF Registration is mandatory for all the establishments-</p>\r\n<ul class=\"p-l-15 ul_f_f list-icon list-icon-arrow list-icon-colored text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		That has engaged 20 or more than 20 people.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		For any other establishment that has less than 20 people then the central government has to specify the same in the notification on the behalf.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	For Employee</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	Employees drawing less than Rs.15000 per month need to mandatorily become members of the EPF. According to the guidelines, employees whose basic pay is more than Rs. 15000 a month at the time of joining are not required to make any PF contributions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	But an employee who is drawing pay of more than Rs.15,000 can still be a member and make contributions with the employer and the Assistant PF commissioner.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	The amount for the contribution of PF</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The employer has to obtain the PF registration within 1 month of attaining the strength, in case of failure to abide by applicable penalties. A registered establishment continues under the purview of the Act even in case the No of employees falls below the required limit.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	The employer has to contribute 12% of the (Basic Salary + Dearness Allowance + Retaining Allowance). An equal amount of contribution is to be made by the employee. If the establishment has engaged less than 20 employees the EPFO rules state that the contribution rate for both the employees and the employer is limited to 10 %. In most cases the employees who are employed in the private sector it is on the basic salary on which the whole contribution is calculated.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	The breakup of the PF contribution</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"p-l-15 ul_f_f list-icon list-icon-arrow list-icon-colored text-justify m-b-30\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 30px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		The 12 % contribution is divided into the following subdivision:</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		3.67% of the contribution towards the Employees Provident Fund</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		1.1% of the contribution towards the EPF administration Charges</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		0.5% of the contribution towards the employee&#39;s deposit linked insurance</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		0.01% contribution towards the EDLI administration charges</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		8.33% towards the Employees Pension Scheme.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.78571em; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251);\">\r\n	What is the Employees Pension Scheme?</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify m-b-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.08px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 249, 251); margin-bottom: 0px !important; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n	8.33% of the employer&rsquo;s contribution is routed towards the Employees Pension Scheme that is calculated at Rs.15,000. The amount routed to the Employee Pension Scheme would be Rs.1250 in case the basic pay of the person is Rs.15,000. If the Basic Pay is less than Rs.15,000 then 8.33% of the amount will be routed and the balance will be retained in the EPF scheme. On superannuation, the employee would receive the full share with the employer&#39;s share reserved for credit in the EPF account.</p>\r\n', 'pf-registration', 'PF Registration', 'PF registration is mandatory for employers having 20 or more employees. Provident Fund (PF) is a social security scheme funded by employees and employers in India.', 'PF Registration in vellore, smart filings, pf registration, provident fund registration, epfo registration, uan registration, pf online apply, pf registration, epf registration, pf registration online, epf registration online, epf grievance registration, register uan, epfo registration online, epf passbook registration, epf register, epfo new registration, uan registration online, epf online register, epf uan registration, epfo member registration, epfigms register grievance, epfo uan registration, uan no registration, epfo online registration, pf uan registration, uan new registration, epf new registration, uan registration and activation, pf register, provident fund registration, online registration of establishment in epfo, epf employer registration, pf grievance registration, epf grievance registration online, register epf account, pf account registration, epfigms register, epfo register grievance, epfo employer registration, uan member registration, register epfo, uan registration epfo, epf member registration, uan registration activation, epfo employee registration, pf registration for employer, epf passbook register, uan registration & activation, pf new registration, uan passbook registration, epf register grievance, pf registration for contractor, employees provident fund registration, epf registration for employee, epfo dsc registration, register for epfo, register pf account, register in epfo, uan registration epf, epf account registration, pf registration for employee, uan activation and registration, epfo registration for employer, uan pf registration, epfo establishment registration, register for uan, uan account registration, online uan registration, epfo registration for employee, register grievance in epfo, epf complaint register, epfo registration uan, uan epfo registration, pf complaint register, epf uan register, epf employer registration online, register for epf passbook, epf company registration, epf dsc registration, establishment registration epfo, pf member registration, member registration epfo, online epfo registration, epf new registration online, epf first time registration, epf passbook register online, epf registration employer, pf employee registration, epfo employer registration online, minimum employee for pf registration, employer registration in epfo, epfindia registration, register epf employer, register uan no, epfo registration online for employer, employee pf registration, esign registration in epfo, pf establishment registration, new epfo registration, pf enrollment, epf establishment registration online, epfo online registration for employer,', 1, 1, 1, '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL);
